item.title: Lost Promises
item.description: And these promises broken, Deep below Each word gets lost in the echo So one last lie I can see through This time I finally let you go…” Lost in the echo, Linkin Park (Living Things) Like millions of others around the world, I am also a die-hard fan of Linkin Park (LP).
